{"tid":1938794,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"保齡球高手求指導","createTime":"2020-03-22T19:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T19:09:17.000Z","uid":325881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9246da521755fd61e0fd6662a53455cc30630f64","tid":1938794,"uid":325881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T19:09:17.000Z","msg":"點先可以拉起隻手唔會好似想跌波咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我打曲球 之前一直無搵過教練<br />\n只係打左咁多年邊打邊睇自學<br />\n終於買左所謂既私家波<br />\n但係出手點都係要左手扶波 <br />\n4步法出手 去到第3步半 左手都係扶緊個波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經拎13磅而我本人係170磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後都係雞翼手出波<br />\n點都做唔到右手係全伸直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拎10磅公家波都係會甩波咁<br />\n以為手指位公家波唔好 專登買私家波都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}